                    <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: center; border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; font-family: 'Marcellus SC', serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, #1e293b 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">Kategori Utama</h2>
                    
